"    <p class=\"headingAnchor2\" id=\"H22\">",
"     <span class=\"h2\">",
"      Finding a lactation consultant",
"     </span>",
"     &nbsp;&mdash;&nbsp;Certified lactation consultants, or LCs, are available at most hospitals as well as privately, and can be an invaluable resource for instructions about breastfeeding, pumping, milk storage, and bottle feeding breast milk. The websites listed below have information about finding a lactation consultant or breastfeeding counselor.",
